PrecisEnactment of the PROVINCIAL EMERGENCIES FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER NO. 51 - which (a) DECLARES the tornado which occurred in the Pine Lake area of ALBERTA on July 14, 2000, to be of concern to the federal government, and (b) AUTHORIZES the provision of financial assistance.
